Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We must be reborn to once again to terrorize this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when the blood of all the hated humans waters the ground like rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we shall again possess the true source of the power of Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l must stop him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,spawned by human suffering from the energy of the planet itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We are reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have had quite a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris is more than capable of taking care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got more guts than a little kid like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When she gets back, l promise to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go back to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,l searched the east wing of the old castle from top to bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no sign of the missing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:03:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Neris?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm having terrible premonitions about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then, a force, strange and unearthly, appeared in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to oppose it, but we were annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And what of Lady Neris?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,l think Lady Neris was among the survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather the soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir! Gather the soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go! Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, this castle was a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh..What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,l don't remember the inside of the castle being like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When was it built?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like a chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Must have been the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that you, Lori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lt was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, it's as we suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the work of no natural beast or human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it all be happening again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke, it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Flare was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Flare was kidnapped by a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get back now, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that you, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing left to worry about, Eon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am l?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones missing from the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that you, Eon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare, how nice of you to come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Eon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Eon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Eon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,l can't believe what's happened to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what may pop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so beautiful, Flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare, l have been waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...since that moment....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll kill you, you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,l can't pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being so late, Prince Zeke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris, you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, l am reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, Flare, shall we go for the coup de grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,l must suck up the energy that pours from your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There, give your energy to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's the stuff that l want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,l will consume your energy, Flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll have your last bit of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke, let me handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hope to defeat me with a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you wish to have me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What have l done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing has taken control of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, while l hold him down, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon? What are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,l'll burn you out of my brain once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,l won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,l won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Release me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Princess Flare?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, l'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm glad you're okay too, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You pathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,l cannot be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as my consciousness remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,l shall never let you go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pitifully tragic existences end so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lt your destiny to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with this kind of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with this short existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All life is still sacred!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The light!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,lmpossible! Flare has taken back her power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,l'm using everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain is glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, Neris!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.87,0:24:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle is crumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.24,0:25:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.81,0:25:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke, Princess Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.09,0:25:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.99,0:26:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.61,0:26:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lf we could be with each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.54,0:26:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just one more time, then l could say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.82,0:26:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye, despite the tears falling from my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.56,0:26:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l would promise never to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.53,0:26:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shape of your sweet smile
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.73,0:26:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l'll carry it with me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.10,0:26:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And keep it always
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But hey
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.57,0:26:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The stars are shining down
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.01,0:26:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They shine down
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.48,0:27:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They shine on and wisper amongst themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.38,0:27:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.12,0:27:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lt will never go
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.86,0:27:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l want to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.56,0:27:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Among the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.40,0:27:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surrounded by cloud dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.87,0:27:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until the day
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.70,0:27:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.17,0:27:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are one
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.94,0:27:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l want to dream
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.65,0:27:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Up in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.41,0:27:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Covered by the starlight, but until then
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.35,0:27:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.32,0:27:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To me again
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.89,0:27:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lf you find
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.46,0:27:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new aurora
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.53,0:27:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Burning up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.70,0:27:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then you'll know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.64,0:28:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That it must be me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.84,0:28:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lf l hear
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.64,0:28:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The stars above
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.31,0:28:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Call me with their whispering
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.25,0:28:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then please
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.29,0:28:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.92,0:28:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again